Global setup:

 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email getvasanth@gmail.com
        

Next steps:

  mkdir QDisplay
  cd QDisplay
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:getvasanth/QDisplay.git
  git push origin master
      
